## Network Topology Graph

An abstract SVG visualization of a design system network.
A circular container (max-width: 450px) with 1px border (#CBD5A0). Central 16px solid Forest node. Three orbiting nodes on dashed paths. Connect nodes to center using 1px solid lines. Animate orbiting nodes.

